### PDF Conversion with Custom Options
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/convert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "pdf",
  "content": "JVBERi0xLjMKJcTl8uXrp/Og0MTGCjQgMCBvYmoKPDwKL0xlbmd0aCA0MSAK...",
  "options": {
    "heading_style": "setext",
    "bullet_list_marker": "*"
  }
}

